 <chunk id="ch60" type="p">
  <sentence id="s60">
   <ns/>
   <tok>
    <orth>,</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>,</base><ctag>interp</ctag></lex>
   </tok>
   <tok>
    <orth>albo</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>albo</base><ctag>conj</ctag></lex>
